em, and exchange titles. The war of the Ethiopians against the Jews of N\'e2gr\'e2n is to be continued by Gabra Mas\uc0\u7731 al or L\'e2l\'eebal\'e2, after his father K\'e2l\'eab has adopted the monastic life in the Monastery of Abb\'e2 Pantalern, and their defeat by him is declared to be a certainty. Parts of the text of this Chapter are difficult to understand.
